creator: Developer Tanitlab
descriptionHtml:
BESS is a FREE android application that stores and allows reporting your business expenses notes.
It is available for Android and iOS devices.
With this app installed in your phone, you can quickly save all your expense notes and report them to your accountant or manager.
The application also allows you to attach a picture of the receipt note.

All expenses are easily categorized.
Mileage expenses are covered.
Receipts picture are stored
A statement of all the transactions can be downloaded to Google Spreadsheet
